      <h2 id="about">About</h2>
      [%PROGRAM%] is a tool to watch / record IPTV streams sent by [%SERVICE%]. 
      It is written in C++ using the <a class="extern" href="http://qt.digia.com" target="_blank">Qt framework by Digia <img src="images/external.png" alt="external" /></a>. 
      The player functionality is realized by using the libvlc library from 
      <a class="extern" href="http://www.videolan.org/vlc/" target="_blank">Videolans VLC player <img src="images/external.png" alt="external" /></a>.
