      <h2 id="versions">Versions</h2>
      There are versions available for:
      <ul>
         <li>Windows (XP or better)</li>
         <li>Mac OSX 10.6 x86_64 or better</li>
         <li>Ubuntu Linux x86 (current version)</li>
      </ul>
      <!-- <div class="toplink"><a href="#top">Top</a></div> -->
      <h2 id="features">Features</h2>
      [%PROGRAM%] has following features:
      <ul>
         <li>play / record live streams</li>
         <li>EPG - electronic program guide</li>
         <li>Archiv - 2 weeks for most channels (play / record)</li>
         <li>Timer Record</li>
         <li>VOD - video on demand (play / record)</li>
         <li>Parental Manager</li>
      </ul>
